<h5>Formatting</h5>
<p>
The content entered for the article's body is processed by a text-formatting
tool before displaying it.  This processing supports a wide variety of styles
such as bold, italic, large-font headlines, etc. as well as things such as
bullet lists and links to other web pages.  The full documentation can be
found in the right hand column of the page whose link follows.  The page that
is immediately linked below contains some of the more common features.
</p>
